==English==

===Noun===

'''planchette'''

#A small [[tablet]] of wood supported on [[caster]]s and having a [[pencil]] attached. The characters produced by the pencil on paper, while the hand rests on the instrument and it is allowed to move, are sometimes translated as of oracular or supernatural import.
